reviewText: I now know that unrated can mean XXX, there is genatalia penetration in this movie. I have often wondered what unrated ment, I now think it means no one has seen this film, it could be G or R or X or XXX. From what was told to me by a movie producer R = nudity, X = simulated sex and XXX = full penetrate. Well my friends be prepared to see XXX content in this movie. That said I think the story is worth the $10.00.
